- Money Tracker Pro is a modern personal finance desktop application built with PySide6 (Qt for Python) and SQLite.
- It helps you track income and expenses, manage savings goals with automatic allocations, visualize monthly trends, and optionally email reports â€” all in a clean, dark UI.




